title: What is Joanna Krupa wearing?
text:
Published October 02, 2015 New York Post Facebook 0 Twitter 0 Email Print
Joanna Krupa is turning cleavage contouring into a thing.
The former “Real Housewives of Miami” star hit PETA’s 35th anniversary bash in Los Angeles on Wednesday in a jewel-encrusted getup that barely covered her lady bits.
Sporting an ultra-revealing YAS Couture gown, Krupa, 36, channeled an overdone southern belle as she stepped-and-repeated her way down the red carpet.
A photo posted by Joanna Krupa (@joannakrupa) on Oct 1, 2015 at 12:09am PDT
And while the reality darling didn’t have any wardrobe malfunctions, she could have used the less-is-more approach when accentuating her assets.
A photo posted by Joanna Krupa (@joannakrupa) on Sep 30, 2015 at 6:05pm PDT
While this evening ensemble may seem a bit shocking to some, it’s just another overstated look in Krupa’s book. Between her cut-out mini dresses and side-boob baring sheaths , don’t expect the recently baptized beauty to cover up anytime soon.
This article originally appeared in the New York Post 's Page Six .
